ygData.subject: RE: [eqbards] Re: Where in Kunark for 27 to 29? (was Charming)
ygData.msgSnippet: I cannot say this too many times.  Lake of Ill Omen.  This place is awesome for xp from 24 to 29th at least.  Most of my guild is here on E ci now, at least
ygData.messageBody:
I cannot say this too many times. Lake of Ill Omen. This place is awesome
for xp from 24 to 29th at least. Most of my guild is here on E'ci now, at
least those in this level range. They are getting 3 bubbles a night and
they are all casual players who play less than 4 hours per night. Goblin
warriors, goblin warlords, sarnak recruits, and charbone and icebone
skeletons are their mane fare.

Kit

Snip: If you need to convince yourself to go to kunark, talk to me.

Okay, I am talking to you Matt. I am on my way to Kunark tonight. I
have heard good things about a few zones. I am currently less than 2
bubbles from 27. Where are some good places to go? I want Charm and
Pixie's!

Thanks,

Piemur Draggonsinger
